<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-07-17T23:59:59-04:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="162" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d162">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>On June 6, 1949, the Senate Committee on Foreign Relations unanimously
                            agreed to report the North Atlantic Treaty to the Senate for favorable
                            action. For text of the Committee’s report, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, June 19, 1949, page 787.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>